{"tid":843404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉霞紐約晤流亡作家余杰展笑容","createTime":"2018-10-01T06:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T08:22:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"791228b7811e35acda578fe9d6a02e70f4fa4b97","tid":843404,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:29:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181001/20511929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F20511929&d=nlBVOU48iSINXS0LVaR%2FY10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=708888bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F20511929&h=c2cf05ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181001/20511929</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月01日 <br />\n<br />\n劉霞紐約晤流亡作家余杰展笑容<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181001/large/a1303a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181001%2Flarge%2Fa1303a.gif&h=3c20f505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作家余杰（左起）、劉霞、劉敏及廖亦武在美國重逢相聚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到美國出席哈維爾基金會活動、諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波的遺孀劉霞，在紐約期間順道與流亡美國的作家余杰見面。余杰昨日在facebook上載兩人合照，並留言：「九年生死兩茫茫，今日相聚何歡暢！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181001/large/a1303b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181001%2Flarge%2Fa1303b.gif&h=b2aff2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉霞展露久違的笑容。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n懷念昔日與劉曉波相聚<br />\n<br />\n現年44歲、2012年流亡美國的余杰，昨日與妻子劉敏及兒子一家三口，從居住的維珍尼亞州前往紐約，與闊別近九年的劉霞、七年未見的廖亦武會面。他表示，當年劉曉波與劉霞前往他在北京的住所，探望其剛出生兒子的情形還歷歷在目，可是「如今，我家兒子已經10歲了。而曉波已經離開我們了」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然留言有點傷感，但余在fb上載的照片所見，他與劉霞、廖亦武等人重聚顯得相當高興，劉霞亦展露久違了的笑容，表現相當愉快。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民都對劉霞能與好友重聚感到十分高興，有網民稱：「這個重逢，要一個正常人為之付出多少代價？」「值得感恩，值得好好慶祝！」也有不少人留言說：「歡迎劉霞來台灣！」對於是否邀劉霞訪台，陸委會副主委邱垂正日前曾經表示，會尊重劉霞的意願，並將會依法處理。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n提早一晚往機場仍塞車<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n河北屋苑疑煤氣爆炸　窗門飛脫5死"},{"pid":"fa8e00bede6441ab501ee8f2b839c35bf594d260","tid":843404,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:55:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe903e1224557a3fcf32d5c48ce86a8c417a4cea","tid":843404,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T08:20:50.000Z","msg":"比共狗逼害到人唔似人 有排醫"},{"pid":"0f7e29eb68913aa6ef9da3e62221158acd020d62","tid":843404,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"一入黎又見 Blocked User <br />\n依家假膠多定5毛多呢?"},{"pid":"ff15efc00b012b78cbd8cd671d8ae9dcbe31adf2","tid":843404,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T08:22:26.000Z","msg":"成功實現中國夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}